		<title>Sales Management-Motivating Sales Teams in Down Markets</title>
		<link>http://bettercloser.com/2008/09/10/sales-management-motivating-sales-teams-in-down-markets/</link>
		<comments>http://bettercloser.com/2008/09/10/sales-management-motivating-sales-teams-in-down-markets/#comments</comments>
